  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section id="faq" style="background:var(--cream);" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="section" style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <p class="section-label">FAQ</p>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="color:var(--bark);">Common <em>questions</em></h2>
      </div>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you offer free estimates? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>Yes! We offer free, no-obligation estimates for all services. Contact us or fill out the form above to request one.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How quickly can you start a project? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>Most projects start within a week of approval. Smaller jobs like mowing or repairs can often be scheduled within 48 hours.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Are you licensed and insured? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>Absolutely. We carry full liability insurance and all work meets local code requirements. We're happy to provide proof upon request.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What areas do you serve? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>We serve Longmont, Boulder, Niwot, and Berthoud. Contact us to see if your area is covered.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Do you offer weekend appointments? <span class="faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>We work Saturday mornings by request. Sunday is our rest day. Contact us to arrange weekend scheduling.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

